Drupal installation made easy. Process:
1. Downloads or detects drupal, unpacks it
2. Downloads libraries
3. Downloads modules (Needs improvement)
4. Setup installation profiles (Manual)

===============================================
CHANGE LOG
===============================================

11-Aug-2012, ver. 0.1.0
Security updates.
Articles renamed to news items. 
Profile now has custom name.
Modules now has subfolder core as opposed to custom for future SymLinks integrtion. (coming soon)

===============================================

29-May-2012, ver. 0.0.8
A. Pre installation
- Options moved to post install step 1 from 2
- Added webform option to enable webform & install default contact form
- Create 'page block' content type to display multi page content
- Disabled 'Promoted' & 'Author & Date' by default for content types

B. Drupal updates
- Module updates: Entity

===============================================

21-May-2012, ver. 0.0.7
A. Commerce template started
B. Drupal updates
- Modules added: Rules, Commerce
- Module updates: Context

===============================================

18-May-2012, ver. 0.0.6
A. Drupal updates
- SEO Modules added: Google Analytics, Meta Tags, XML site map
- Module updates: Admin menu, features
B. Code updates:
- Installation complete
- - Take care of .htaccess, cookie issue
- - Copy & modify installation profile
- - Copy drupal & delete installation files

===============================================

16-May-2012, ver. 0.0.5
A. Drupal updates
- Libraries updated: CSS3Pie 5 beta to 1.0.0
- Module updates: webform, pathauto, token
B. Code updates:
- Generic URL when redirecting from index.php

===============================================

08-May-2012, ver. 0.0.3
A. Reference to Drupal version is generic now apart from default function parameter values
B. Updates:
- Core update 7.12 to 7.14
- Libraries updated: CKEditor 3.6.2 to 3.6.3
- Module updates: CSS3PIE, AdminMenu, Migrate & Backup, CKEditor, entity (1.0-rc1 to 1.0-rc2)
- Modules added: FontYourFace, Views Slideshow, Omega Theme Modules (Context, Delta, Omega Tools), Devel, Features, Entity, Override node options
C. Update to static instalation profile

===============================================

05-May-2012, ver. 0.0.1
 - Initial release: downloads Drupal 7.12, downloads CKEditor, creates libraries folder
 
